item.description:
Our Fifth Wednesday Groups for OPEN MEN are Community Nights!

You are welcome to come and have some fun with us at the CENTRAL ROCK GYM in Hadley MA on Wednesday Aug 29 beginning at 6:30pm. We will be doing a 1.5 hour assisted climb and a 1/2 hour of time in the Social Area at the gym.

COST is $25 per person.

NO EXPERIENCE NEEDED! None of us are rock climbers - we just want to go have some fun and push our limits for a while in the company of good men. Join us!! This will be a super low risk way to meet some of the men of OPEN MEN and have a good time!

group.name: Open Men's Group - Personal Mastery Workgroup

item.name: FIFTH WEDNESDAY - ROCK CLIMBING at Central Rock in Hadley!
